---
import ProjectDetailsPage from "@/components/pages/ProjectDetailsPage.astro";
---

<ProjectDetailsPage projectId="free" locale="en">
  <h2>About Free</h2>
  <p>
    Free is a native macOS application designed to help you regain focus and
    manage your screen time effectively. It features strict allowlist
    enforcement, wildcard website blocking rules, weekly schedules, Pomodoro
    cycles, and calendar import. Designed with a tamper-resistant strict mode,
    it ensures you stay committed to your focus sessions.
  </p>
  <p>
    For detailed configuration instructions, advanced features, and
    troubleshooting, please check the <a
      href="https://github.com/albibenni/free#readme"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener">official README on GitHub</a
    >.
  </p>

  <h2>Installation</h2>

  <h3>Download .dmg</h3>
  <p>You can download the latest version of Free directly:</p>
  <p>
    <a
      href="https://github.com/albibenni/free/releases/latest/download/Free.dmg"
      class="not-prose inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white no-underline shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600"
    >
      <svg
        class="mr-2 -ml-1 h-5 w-5"
        fill="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 384 512"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        <path
          d="M318.7 268.7c-.2-36.7 16.4-64.4 50-84.8-18.8-26.9-47.2-41.7-84.7-44.6-35.5-2.8-74.3 20.7-88.5 20.7-15 0-49.4-19.7-76.4-19.7C63.3 141.2 22.1 184.4 4 273.5q-9 49.3 15.3 104.9c13.7 30 35.5 68.3 71.2 68.3 33.7 0 46-21.7 85.5-21.7 39 0 48.7 21.7 85.5 21.7 39.4 0 65.5-44.2 80-72.3 26.6-51.2 5.3-95.2-22.8-105.8zM245.9 83c36.1-41.8 28.5-83 28.5-83-36.1 2.3-70 21.7-93.5 54.3-17.6 23.9-30 52-25.7 82.5 37.9 3.5 70.8-23.7 90.7-53.8z"
        ></path>
      </svg>
      Download Free.dmg
    </a>
  </p>

  <h3>Homebrew</h3>
  <p>Alternatively, you can install Free via Homebrew:</p>
  <pre><code>brew install albibenni/tap/free</code></pre>
</ProjectDetailsPage>
